+| Test Type | Pattern | Example |
+|-----------|---------|---------|
+| **Unit Tests** | Table-driven, real fixtures | Skill parsing, template rendering |
+| **Integration Tests** | Real filesystem, temp dirs | Skill installation, config loading |
